p.k: Think About Your Future / Booty Scooty / Who's Laughing Now / Oregon Trail The Titans are reckless with their money and health much to the detriment of their future selves. / In order to save Titans Tower from some wealthy land developers, the Titans search for pirate treasure. / Beast Boy decides to find his spirit animal and joins a group of bears. / The Titans get into the pioneer spirit as they head west on the Oregon Trail.
